author: Leonardo da Vinci
message: In rivers, the water that you touch is the last of what has passed and the first of that which comes; so with present time.
title: Thought of the day

author: Byron Pulsifer
message: Spring is a time for rebirth and the fulfilment of new life.
title: Thought of the day

message: There is nothing happens to any person but what was in his power to go through with.
